Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}背後抵住捲簾大門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}指先は鉄の匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}指尖充滿金屬腥氣
