Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:36.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}find a way　ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:36.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}find a way　從此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:41.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}found out　見つける
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:41.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}found out　將其找尋
