Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:47.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}奏響rock
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:52.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}遠くを見据えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:52.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}望向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}息継ぎさえできない街の中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}那令人窒息的道路之中
